Please come into my heart and help me.

38:53.698 --> 38:59.427
by the power of the Holy Spirit to trust and to live for you.

39:00.849 --> 39:01.190
Amen.

39:01.771 --> 39:02.071
Amen.

39:02.091 --> 39:02.993
Let's congratulate.

39:06.678 --> 39:09.843
Amazing.

39:09.863 --> 39:11.025
Now we've got a gift for you.

39:12.527 --> 39:17.355
It's actually a new version of the Gospel of John, which we're introducing to the church today.

39:17.375 --> 39:19.098
And this is Ben and Patricia over here.

39:19.118 --> 39:19.739
It just gives away.

39:19.779 --> 39:21.842
There are service leaders for this service.

39:21.954 --> 39:24.478
And they're going to be in the chapel.

39:24.498 --> 39:25.359
We've got a little chapel there.

39:25.379 --> 39:26.962
I'm going to give you a gift and help you.

39:26.982 --> 39:31.990
I'm going to jump off the stage and shake every single one of your hands because this is such a special moment.

39:32.511 --> 39:33.312
So I want to give you two.

39:33.432 --> 39:35.075
I want to give you two little pieces of advice.

39:35.856 --> 39:37.759
Number one, keep coming back to church.

39:38.780 --> 39:39.782
Keep coming back to church.

39:40.383 --> 39:43.728
Number two, every day, just read a few verses from this Bible.

39:44.469 --> 39:47.474
It will help you fuel your faith for the coming days.

39:47.586 --> 39:49.509
We're going to sing that song, the greatness of the Lord.

39:49.549 --> 39:51.693
As we do, I'm going to jump down and shake all of your hands.

39:51.893 --> 39:52.734
Why don't you come this way?

39:52.794 --> 39:57.482
Come on.

39:57.502 --> 40:06.316
Let's stretch our hands towards every person who's made that decision today.

40:06.336 --> 40:08.239
Father God, you see every hand.

40:08.760 --> 40:09.581
You see every heart.

40:10.543 --> 40:15.090
We pray right now for every person who's making a decision to become a follower of Jesus.

40:15.682 --> 40:16.684
that they would walk with you.

40:16.704 --> 40:17.626
They would talk with you.

40:18.287 --> 40:21.012
They would be close to you Father God every step of the way.

40:21.774 --> 40:23.417
We thank you Lord.

40:23.437 --> 40:25.180
Today they rewrite their story.

40:25.922 --> 40:30.611
Today their story has got a new chapter and a brighter future in Jesus name.

40:30.951 --> 40:31.993
Now celebrate church.

40:32.494 --> 40:33.536
Come on let's celebrate.

40:37.885 --> 40:38.546
Thank you Lord.

40:57.666 --> 41:01.432
The service just said yes to Jesus.

41:01.452 --> 41:05.318
The greatness of the Lord is beyond compare.

41:06.920 --> 41:07.281
Amen.

41:08.803 --> 41:14.511
Well, we've heard how we get to share it now.

41:14.532 --> 41:21.562
It's on us now for his spirit to step out and have a flood of Amazon delivery drivers.

41:23.044 --> 41:24.326
The front here next Sunday.

41:25.889 --> 41:26.770
Fantastic.

41:27.074 --> 41:27.935
at prime for it.

41:33.422 --> 41:34.663
Thanks again for tuning in.

41:35.404 --> 41:47.780
If you said yes to Jesus today by saying the salvation prayer, we'd love for you to email connections at soulchurch.com so we can talk to you a little bit more about this incredible decision you've just made.

41:48.420 --> 41:56.210
And if at any point in the service you felt moved to give towards any of our local or global initiatives, head to soulchurch.com.

41:56.642 --> 42:03.696
And don't forget to stay connected with us on Facebook, Instagram and YouTube by searching at Soul Church UK.

42:04.299 --> 42:05.746
Take care and God bless.

